snippet.title: Crescent County - Official Reveal Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Here's your look at the announcement trailer for Crescent County. Check out the trailer to see gameplay, characters, and the colorful world of this game that's coming to Xbox and Steam.

Credit: The trailer features the song 'I'm Not Getting Excited' by The Beths by Carpark Records
